embeds.title: What is Dcordlink?
embeds.description:
Dcordlink is a platform that gives you a free way to get custom discord invite vanity urls. Completely for **free**.

You can get Analytics  about your invite link, and make your own embed, with colors & description.

embeds.title: FAQ's
embeds.description: Many asked questions will be answered here.

fields.name: Can i make my invite link private from the discover page?
fields.value: Yes, under settings you can chose privacy.

fields.name: My embed is not updating?
fields.value: If your embeddoes not update immediately, you may have to wait a few minutes for discord to update your embed. If more than an hour has passed you can make a ticket, then you will get help.

fields.name: Is this 100% free?
fields.value: Yes, its a 100% free service to use. But you can only have 3 links per account.

fields.name: Is my data safe?
fields.value: Your data is 100% secure with us, so you do not have to worry.
